  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/b57809a8facc3dc456ebc19b5821ec7b.avif?t=1751451925\" width=750 height=86 /></span>Join our Discord community and get more events  details in group! Find the Discord link in the sidebar.</p></p><br><h1>Download the Full Version</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/50d16c6e4383e4d0b553f4c6be8f045b.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/50d16c6e4383e4d0b553f4c6be8f045b.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search \"Horror Simulator VR\" and add the full version to your cart!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/4ec8c1b74a8793746b4d6cd85a9073e3.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A <strong>classic ghost-hunting</strong> game packed with <strong>puzzles, sudden scares, and fun co-op chases,</strong> <strong>that becomes one of the most popular Multiplayer horror games.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get full game Horror Simulator VR to unlock more maps & content and have even more fun and thrills!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻Play with squad, chase&catch the demon (Easy Peasy!!)</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find the Room</strong>: Use your light to spot unusual objects, listen to whispers… is the demon room nearby?</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Items&Props</strong>: Throw <strong>Holy Water</strong> to find demon shadows! Hold a <strong>Cross</strong> to track footsteps! Lots of tools to play!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find the demon's name: Solve puzzles of demon’s name. Find the right items and put them on the platform. Hurry up!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RUN OR HIDE</strong>: Hide in closets, scare demons away with the <strong>Bible</strong>. <strong>More Power-up props</strong> to fight demons, so much FUN!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️Why So Fun?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactions</strong>: Push the doors, answer phone calls, play the piano... Real scenes, explore freely!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice Chat</strong>: Chat with teammates while running. After being killed, become a ghost to give your friends clues!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coin Frenzy</strong>: Earn coins by completing missions to buy <strong>Freddie bear masks</strong>, angel avatars, and dress up as the coolest!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️FREE Version? Still AWESOME!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Big Mansion map + Classic Mode</strong> - Team up with friends for all-night multiplayer sessions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join Discord to unlock Crazy Mode</strong> - Join Discord to unlock Crazy Mode - Fight 10 amazing demon powers!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️If You're Addicted to...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heart-pounding chase from Animal Company, Noclip VR, Yeeps - our hunting system will make you go crazy! Demons can climb, break doors, and even pretend to be your friend.</p>",
